<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="abroad-adv">abroad <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /əˈbrɔːd/    美 /əˈbrɔːd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在 / 到国外；在 / 到海外：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>go abroad</strong> for further study
出国深造</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>travel / live abroad
出国旅行/住在国外</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Although he is known to only a few people here, his reputation abroad is very great.
虽然这里只有几个人知道他，但他在国外的名气却很大。</p><footer>2015 湖北</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The books about Harry Potter are very popular now,both <strong>at home and abroad</strong>. 
有关哈利·波特的书目前在国内外都很流行。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She had just returned <strong>from abroad</strong>. 她刚从国外回来。
她刚从国外回来。</p><footer>2015 重庆改</footer></div></div>